293
00:18:55,290 --> 00:18:57,980
His bracelet or his heart?

294
00:18:59,770 --> 00:19:00,770
His bracelet.

295
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:08,830
What haven’t you told us?

296
00:19:09,790 --> 00:19:11,490
