318
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,200
Hmm.

319
00:21:03,140 --> 00:21:06,690
I guess I’d be a little sad.

320
00:21:09,950 --> 00:21:11,660
But don’t think that far ahead.

321
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:14,340
You might find your answer tomorrow.

322
00:21:16,090 --> 00:21:17,310
I hope so.

323
00:21:19,910 --> 00:21:21,080
Please wait for me.

324
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:23,980
♪ If this is truly real ♪

325
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:26,640
♪ This love, I pray ♪

326
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:31,900
