327
00:21:45,340 --> 00:21:46,250
Sleep well.

328
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:48,770
No good or bad dreams.

329
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:58,720
♪ No one else, just you ♪

330
00:22:11,910 --> 00:22:12,870
What are you doing?

331
00:22:13,210 --> 00:22:14,610
I brought breakfast for my buddy.

332
00:22:15,620 --> 00:22:16,460
Buddy?

333
00:22:16,470 --> 00:22:17,080
Mm.

334
00:22:17,390 --> 00:22:18,660
Please.

335
00:22:19,300 --> 00:22:22,380
People forgot about the buddy thing
since the first week of the activity.

336
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,890
You guys are still doing it?

337
00:22:24,320 --> 00:22:24,920
No.

338
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:26,730
Then why are you in my room?

339
00:22:26,740 --> 00:22:28,040
No more sticking your nose in my business.

340
00:22:33,210 --> 00:22:34,300
Okay.

341
00:22:34,870 --> 00:22:36,220
I’ll stay out of it,

342
00:22:36,740 --> 00:22:39,020
but you should be grateful to me

343
00:22:39,610 --> 00:22:44,080
for leaving the door unlocked
and letting the puppy’s owner come hug it every night.

344
00:22:44,670 --> 00:22:45,510
I’m leaving.

345
00:22:45,850 --> 00:22:46,780
I won’t get in your business.

346
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:49,490
You don’t want me to, so I won’t,

347
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:51,000
