348
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:53,120
Make yourself at home in my room.

349
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,410
Do whatever you want.

350
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:55,900
I’m leaving now.

351
00:22:55,930 --> 00:22:57,240
Bye.

352
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:58,900
Okay, fine.

353
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:07,780
You’re playing buddies?

354
00:23:08,290 --> 00:23:09,990
No, I just wanted to see you,

355
00:23:10,010 --> 00:23:11,610
but couldn’t think of an excuse.

356
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:14,670
Now that you’re wearing the jacket
and don’t need the tie,

357
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,550
