358
00:23:18,550 --> 00:23:19,410
Do I look handsome?

359
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,660
I’ve seen you in this before.

360
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:28,370
I’m asking if I look handsome.

361
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:33,770
So?

362
