Pretty good.

363
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:43,800
Are you staying to drink that with me?

364
00:23:44,050 --> 00:23:45,240
I’ll get you a glass.

365
00:23:45,260 --> 00:23:47,650
Mm, we can go to class together.

366
