Hey, what are these?

387
00:24:43,790 --> 00:24:45,760
Faifa’s birthday gifts.

388
00:24:46,740 --> 00:24:47,650
Is it your birthday today?

389
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:49,490
Yes, dude.

390
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:51,240
No need to order lunch.

391
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:52,990
