392
00:24:53,010 --> 00:24:53,820
Whoa.

393
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,610
Who are you?

394
00:24:55,630 --> 00:24:58,560
How are you going to bring all these gifts back?

395
00:24:58,660 --> 00:25:00,160
I have you guys,

396
00:25:00,180 --> 00:25:01,510
