430
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:28,930
So today is like another birthday for Yotha?

431
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:30,860
I guess you could say that.

432
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:33,240
He probably remembers that today is his birthday.

433
00:26:37,620 --> 00:26:38,620
Are you done with classes?

434
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,800
Yes.

435
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:41,490
What are you doing?

436
00:26:42,230 --> 00:26:43,280
Well,

437
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,730
I’m missing you, Arc.

438
00:26:46,060 --> 00:26:47,020
Where are you going?

439
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:48,490
Hmm.

440
00:26:49,410 --> 00:26:51,890
I’m probably going to keep missing you.

441
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:53,330
Hey!

442
00:26:54,090 --> 00:26:55,550
If you’re going to be like this,

443
00:26:55,570 --> 00:26:57,970
