444
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,450
Can I?

445
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:01,010
I’m being sarcastic!

446
00:27:01,020 --> 00:27:02,080
He’s being sarcastic!

447
00:27:02,100 --> 00:27:03,340
Come on.

448
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:08,810
We’re going to work on our project at your place.

449
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:10,500
I hope that’s okay.

450
00:27:10,730 --> 00:27:11,750
Go ahead.

451
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:12,990
Take care of each other.

452
00:27:13,250 --> 00:27:16,870
Oh, no one takes better care of me than you.

453
00:27:16,890 --> 00:27:18,520
Please hurry back.

454
00:27:18,540 --> 00:27:19,590
I miss you.

455
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:22,420
Yeah.

456
00:27:22,730 --> 00:27:23,480
Kisses.

457
00:27:23,760 --> 00:27:24,810
Talk tonight.

458
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:26,280
Yes, babe.

459
00:27:26,300 --> 00:27:27,180
See you soon.

460
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,710
Muah.

461
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:32,380
I’ll talk to you tonight, babe.

462
00:27:33,300 --> 00:27:34,680
Hey, I have my sweetheart.

463
00:27:34,700 --> 00:27:35,500
I can’t talk to you.

464
00:27:37,850 --> 00:27:39,350
