465
00:27:40,130 --> 00:27:40,600
Look at you.

466
00:27:40,620 --> 00:27:41,900
Oh, no.

467
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:43,040
You must be lonely.

468
00:27:57,660 --> 00:27:58,370
I’m itchy.

469
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,280
Hey, Yotha.

470
00:28:02,490 --> 00:28:03,710
