474
00:28:14,540 --> 00:28:15,330
Open it.

475
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:21,020
A necktie?

476
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:22,760
Yeah.

477
00:28:23,410 --> 00:28:25,570
I didn’t know what to get you.

478
00:28:25,890 --> 00:28:27,370
You already have everything

479
00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:30,060
