507
00:30:43,500 --> 00:30:44,750
Just go.

508
00:30:45,100 --> 00:30:46,480
Hurry.

509
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:50,380
I’m going then.

510
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,090
Mm.

511
00:30:53,090 --> 00:30:54,180
