527
00:31:30,670 --> 00:31:31,310
Hey!

528
00:31:31,330 --> 00:31:32,200
Fai!

529
00:31:32,580 --> 00:31:34,220
Why do you keep cursing my business?

530
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:34,890
That’s great.

531
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:37,090
How about you, Faifa?

532
00:31:37,110 --> 00:31:39,610
