876
00:57:27,160 --> 00:57:28,691
I’m not jealous anymore.

877
00:57:32,410 --> 00:57:33,377
I’m just possessive.

878
00:57:34,840 --> 00:57:37,291
Especially these eyes of yours…

879
00:57:39,780 --> 00:57:41,291
I’m so possessive of them.

880
00:57:45,030 --> 00:57:46,028
You’re crazy.

881
00:57:46,468 --> 00:57:48,460
Yes, and you’re crazy.

882
00:58:52,280 --> 00:58:57,440
♪ I won't believe in love they say is true ♪

883
00:58:57,468 --> 00:59:03,548
♪ Each time it comes, it never feels right ♪

884
00:59:04,160 --> 00:59:11,902
♪ Chance is getting slim, I’m closing up inside ♪

885
00:59:20,165 --> 00:59:21,900
I thought you were going home this weekend.

886
00:59:22,580 --> 00:59:23,600
I have a headache.

887
00:59:23,622 --> 00:59:24,794
I can’t drive.

888
00:59:25,570 --> 00:59:26,211
What’s wrong?

889
00:59:26,640 --> 00:59:27,645
Do you have any medicine?

890
00:59:28,057 --> 00:59:28,994
Yes.

891
00:59:29,520 --> 00:59:30,365
Here it is.

892
00:59:30,890 --> 00:59:31,897
You can go.

893
00:59:32,280 --> 00:59:33,588
Call me if you need anything.

894
00:59:33,600 --> 00:59:34,914
I’ll turn the ringer on.

895
00:59:35,570 --> 00:59:36,531
Okay.

896
00:59:36,548 --> 00:59:37,302
See you.

897
00:59:37,970 --> 00:59:39,120
Get well soon.

898
00:59:39,142 --> 00:59:40,222
Mm.

899
01:00:05,720 --> 01:00:06,520
Gun!

900
01:00:20,770 --> 01:00:21,897
Are you okay?

901
01:00:24,817 --> 01:00:25,714
I’m fine.

902
01:00:28,720 --> 01:00:29,542
Whoa.

903
01:00:30,250 --> 01:00:31,417
You’re not fine.

904
01:00:31,411 --> 01:00:32,851
You’re burning up.

905
01:00:35,700 --> 01:00:37,417
I can take care of myself.

906
01:00:38,920 --> 01:00:40,685
I’m just going to buy some medicine.

907
01:00:51,350 --> 01:00:52,554
I don’t want to eat congee.

908
01:00:52,980 --> 01:00:54,160
Then what do you want to eat?

909
01:00:57,270 --> 01:00:58,394
Takoyaki.

910
01:00:58,577 --> 01:00:59,634
No.

911
01:01:01,900 --> 01:01:03,491
Can I have cold water?

912
01:01:04,120 --> 01:01:05,142
Also no.

913
01:01:27,560 --> 01:01:28,480
I’m full.

914
01:01:29,760 --> 01:01:30,897
That’s all you’re going to eat?

915
01:01:32,420 --> 01:01:34,034
I’ll give you a pass this time,

916
01:01:34,780 --> 01:01:36,577
but next meal, you have to eat at least half a bowl.

917
01:01:52,480 --> 01:01:53,502
Have you swallowed the pills?

918
01:01:55,782 --> 01:01:56,617
Yes.

919
01:02:05,430 --> 01:02:06,542
Do you want me to hug you?

920
01:02:11,130 --> 01:02:12,205
No, it’s fine.

921
01:02:14,554 --> 01:02:15,885
Let me rephrase that.

922
01:02:19,970 --> 01:02:21,405
Can I hug you?

923
01:02:44,730 --> 01:02:45,920
You might get sick too.

924
01:02:46,330 --> 01:02:47,114
I’m not afraid.

925
01:02:53,770 --> 01:02:54,662
Yotha.

926
01:02:55,410 --> 01:02:55,988
Hmm?

927
01:02:59,897 --> 01:03:01,890
You haven’t figured out the answer, have you?

928
01:03:04,660 --> 01:03:05,148
Mm.

929
01:03:09,720 --> 01:03:10,771
It’s okay.

930
01:03:12,240 --> 01:03:14,028
But can I take back what I said?

931
01:03:17,725 --> 01:03:18,731
I said that

932
01:03:22,834 --> 01:03:25,154
if someone makes you love them more than me,

933
01:03:26,380 --> 01:03:27,714
you’re free to go.

934
01:03:30,460 --> 01:03:31,885
Can I ask you not to go anymore?

935
01:03:33,700 --> 01:03:35,377
I don’t plan on going anywhere.

936
01:03:36,720 --> 01:03:39,800
♪ Never imagined ♪

937
01:03:39,828 --> 01:03:42,251
♪ This could be real ♪

938
01:03:42,280 --> 01:03:45,068
♪ Feels like a dream ♪

939
01:03:45,085 --> 01:03:47,731
♪ If this is truly real ♪

940
01:03:47,754 --> 01:03:50,422
♪ This love, I pray ♪

941
01:03:50,462 --> 01:03:55,720
♪ Will be the last to stay ♪

942
01:03:58,010 --> 01:04:03,405
♪ Now you have me, no more feeling lonely ♪

943
01:04:03,428 --> 01:04:06,085
♪ There’ll always be you in every story ♪

944
01:04:06,108 --> 01:04:09,720
♪ I’ll hold your faith and help you see ♪

945
01:04:09,748 --> 01:04:12,337
♪ What true love is like ♪

946
01:04:12,348 --> 01:04:17,662
♪ I want you to forever stay by my side ♪

947
01:04:17,685 --> 01:04:21,114
♪ No one else, just you ♪

948
01:04:28,388 --> 01:04:32,445
♪ No one else, just you ♪

949
01:04:33,131 --> 01:04:34,217
I want to take care of him.

950
01:04:34,720 --> 01:04:36,034
I want him to smile every day.

951
01:04:36,380 --> 01:04:37,348
There you go.

952
01:04:37,365 --> 01:04:39,908
Now you know
you love him.

953
01:04:40,480 --> 01:04:41,571
Let’s go to your house, Beagle.

954
01:04:42,730 --> 01:04:43,760
Tell me honestly.

955
01:04:44,051 --> 01:04:45,200
Is he your friend or your boyfriend?

956
01:04:45,342 --> 01:04:46,737
I’m trying to win Gun’s heart.

957
01:04:47,440 --> 01:04:48,571
I’m brave now.

958
01:04:48,860 --> 01:04:49,405
Huh?

959
01:04:50,028 --> 01:04:51,702
I’m brave enough to love you, Beagle.

960
01:04:53,700 --> 01:04:54,902
Will you be my boyfriend?
